41
00:02:50.620 --> 00:02:52.630
Whatever. losers. Enjoy your soda.

42
00:02:52.710 --> 00:02:54.670
At least we're old enough to drink.

43
00:02:54.750 --> 00:02:56.300
Hey. can you guys keep it down out here?

44
